{"tid":514527,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)異次元殺陣/心慌方1-3","createTime":"2017-12-30T16:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T19:21:12.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"203f4b61b11b6cb63df5be9990050eedaf11b84a","tid":514527,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=iDzVAHoAp7BrWJAoeKcibWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=ce7b397d\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=iDzVAHoAp7BrWJAoeKcibWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=584474e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/0/0c/Cube_The_Movie_Poster_Art.jpg/220px-Cube_The_Movie_Poster_Art.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F0%2F0c%2FCube_The_Movie_Poster_Art.jpg%2F220px-Cube_The_Movie_Poster_Art.jpg&h=f60144d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.整個迷宮中的每一個立方體要麼是安全的，要麼是裝有致命的危險設備（比如能夠把進入的人切成碎塊的「壽司機器」或者能夠向進入的人噴射強酸性液體的裝置）。起初，人們往想要進入的立方體扔一個綁著繩子的靴子，以測試該立方體是否安全，但是這個方法很快就失效了，Rennes，綽號Wren&mdash;&mdash;一個曾經逃脫六、七個高科技保安監獄的越獄專家，恐怖地在一個通過「靴子測試」的立方體房間中受到致命的襲擊，當人們把他拉回上一個房間時死亡<br />\n<br />\n2.影片講述了一個盲女，一個電腦遊戲設計師，一個物理學家，一個建築工程師，一個私家偵探，一個漂亮女律師，一個精神科醫生和一個五角大樓上校，八個城中專業人士，一天醒來，赫然發現身處一個神秘密室，無人知道這是何等地方，眼前的只是一班完全不相識的人...<br />\n<br />\n3.本片是《心慌方》系列的前傳，影片更加詳盡地解釋了巨大、神秘、致命的立方體迷宮從何而來， 以及為什麼會有人被綁架、囚禁到其中，影片中的主角到了結尾，也被放到了立方體迷宮內。 《心慌方3》裡的主角就是對應著《心慌方1》裡面出場的&ldquo;'天才'傻子&rdquo;。<br />\n對於厄尼&middot;巴巴拉什主觀的評價安德烈&middot;塞庫拉執導的前作《超立方體》&ldquo;差強人意&rdquo;，被業內諷為忘恩負義，《超立方體》獨特的明亮氣氛增強了立方體主題的空靈，盡量減少使人噁心的道具出現，就連鮮血也局限在偵探身上，所有不可避免的&ldquo;恐怖因素&quot;被導演演繹的近乎完美，尤其是後半部分出現的屍體道具，木乃伊般的幽古，襯托著明亮的立方體現代空間..<br />\n<br />\n12 15AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=iDzVAHoAp7BrWJAoeKcibWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=2baa7471\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=iDzVAHoAp7BrWJAoeKcibWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=9d930ecc\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b7cac7a6f88f71faab44dd4a3f040eaf7ec59d","tid":514527,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120ba6d35d4504ac7eaf009fd5742741a2ae8ca0","tid":514527,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:17:22.000Z","msg":"得一好睇<br />\n二都唔知做乜鳩"},{"pid":"0fd6e6d84454ec6d3acf4b130bbd703b75e9cfb6","tid":514527,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77bb332b